txt.en: Defeat the Harbinger of the Dead in \qDoom of Caras Gelebren\q
One of the Harbingers of the Dead, a terrible omen of death and decay, has come to this place.

Defeat the Harbinger of the Dead in \qDoom of Caras Gelebren\q.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: Do not retreat from combat.</rgb>
